Short name:    selenized_black_white
Author:        Daniel Gray <dng@disroot.org>
Maintainer:    Jan Warcho≈Ç <jan.warchol@gmail.com>
Website:       https://github.com/jan-warchol/selenized
Description:   Selenized color palette - balanced colors for your terminal
License:       MIT
